<div class="big-bg">
  <div class="container">
    <h1>家計簿APP</h1>
    <h2>~HouseHold Account Book~</h2>
    <p>シンプルな家計簿アプリです。収入、支出を管理してPrimaryBalanceを確認しましょう。</p>
    <% if session[:user].nil? %>
      <button type="button" class="btn btn-info btn-lg mr-5 mt-5" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#signup">Signup</button>
      <button type="button" class="btn btn-success btn-lg mt-5" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#login">Login</button>
    <% else %>
      <a class="nav-link ml-3" href="javascript:logout.submit()">
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary btn-lg mt-5">Logout</button>
      </a>
    <% end %>
  </div>
</div>